{"tid":1855594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"笑撚死，又話屠村燒村，元朗班叔父都未撚驚過","createTime":"2020-02-01T07:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T18:27:52.000Z","uid":240250,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"effac064dfaf0c6150eb6e460eb17b53c3ffbc01","tid":1855594,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:24:18.000Z","msg":"成班垃圾，打你咪打你"},{"pid":"1138d5b4d7cf9017d2d2a2c354ed515eb8c2236c","tid":1855594,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:35:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2HD3SzD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2HD3SzD.jpg&h=e01c6f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#standwithHAEA<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/c/1352779856/117585\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fc%2F1352779856%2F117585&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=f38d0e2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/c/1352779856/117585</a>"},{"pid":"2e876974b2d65c594cbbef03e929779c2360a0e7","tid":1855594,"uid":54517,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:40:54.000Z","msg":"會員 #240250 - 徐永強 極有可能係五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍<br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n我正式宣布，大家休息至立法會選舉！！！ - #1<br />\n前線手足嘅血汗總算有回報，大家記住沉著冷靜，唔好再開花，免得令民意逆轉！記住血債票償呀！要喺體制內打贏佢哋！<br />\n嚟！一齊叫！光復香港，時代革命！<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1756452/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1756452/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人終於贏左第一仗！多謝勇武手足，你地終於可以退下火線 - #1<br />\n首先多謝各位前線勇武手足，你地嘅血汗已經化為選票，我哋幫你報咗仇。<br />\n區選大勝，證明民意喺我哋呢邊，我哋下一步就係要建立黃色經濟圈，<br />\n等啲黃店發大嚟搞，請返留咗案底嘅手足，再下一步就係贏埋立法會選舉。<br />\n現階段抗爭運動正式轉形，最緊要唔好再搞以下幾樣野，<br />\n因為太影響民生或者畫面唔好睇，有可能會令民意反彈：<br />\n1. 堵路<br />\n2. 火魔<br />\n3. 裝修<br />\n4. 神獸<br />\n5. 黎明行動<br />\n6. 三罷<br />\n想繼續表達訴求嘅可以考慮星期日搞下遊行集會（記得要有不反），<br />\n記住唔好影響市民，唔好失民意，最好做咗都冇人知！<br />\nCome on！光復香港！時代革命！[img]<a href=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gilihkg.com/thread/1755038/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gilihkg.com%2Fthread%2F1755038%2Fpage%2F1%3Fref%3Dsharer%26post%3D1&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=5577bfa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gilihkg.com/thread/1755038/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n運動已完，大家請接受現實 - #1<br />\n打左幾個月而家先返轉頭玩和理非玩感化，一定冇noise。林鄭嘅策略簡單暴力，但非常成功地將前線拉得七七八八，剩返嗰班和理非不足為患（其實對家由頭到尾都冇放和理非在眼內），就由得你喺度圍爐打飛機，打多排冇癮就自己散。<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1743386/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1743386/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請立即停止黎明行動！ - #1<br />\n黎明左咁多日，打工仔都適應哂，要返工嘅早兩個鐘出門口爬山都會返工，最多係遲一兩個鐘，但再搞落去只會令打工仔屌聲四起，增加民鬥民嘅情況。我呼籲大家立即停止黎明行動，準時返工返學方為上策。<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1740561/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1740561/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布黎明行動唔撚使再搞 - #1<br />\n好簡單既道理：一鼓作氣，再而衰，三而竭。<br />\n所有招數都係用一次，唔食住上星期個勢搞落去就唔使旨意再搞，你不妨睇下呢場運動有咩招數係停完之後再攞返出黎用係work既？<br />\n<a href=\"http://所以各位準時返工啦lihkg.com/thread/1737015/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%89%80%E4%BB%A5%E5%90%84%E4%BD%8D%E6%BA%96%E6%99%82%E8%BF%94%E5%B7%A5%E5%95%A6lihkg.com%2Fthread%2F1737015%2Fpage%2F1%3Fref%3Dsharer%26post%3D1&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=c0c5767b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">所以各位準時返工啦lihkg.com/thread/1737015/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a>"},{"pid":"596c3f535b594a2d3135aa3daebb247a3b587025","tid":1855594,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2